My meeting got canceled.

44
00:02:36,406 --> 00:02:39,409
Didn't you take a shower this morning?

45
00:02:39,409 --> 00:02:41,995
I, uh, I just finished a workout.

46
00:02:41,995 --> 00:02:43,705
Where's John?

47
00:02:43,705 --> 00:02:45,290
John?

48
00:02:45,290 --> 00:02:47,918
Yeah. That's his truck out front.

49
00:02:47,918 --> 00:02:49,711
Gabrielle was panicked.

50
00:02:49,711 --> 00:02:52,089
She knew if her husband discovered her secret,

51
00:02:52,089 --> 00:02:55,092
she would feel the full force of his wrath.

52
00:02:56,009 --> 00:02:59,012
Hey, mr. Solis.

53
00:02:59,179 --> 00:03:01,807
Hey, John, take care of that ficus yet?

54
00:03:01,807 --> 00:03:04,810
- I'll get to it as soon as I'm done here.
- All right.

55
00:03:07,312 --> 00:03:10,107
- But she was quickly reminded that...
